text: This recently remodeled charmer on a fully fenced lot is sure to suit all your needs. With New carpet, interior paint, plumbing fixtures, light fixtures and appliances, this home is move-in-ready. There is plenty of space with 4 total bedrooms and a bonus room for office, entertainment, whatever your heart desires! Located in a lovely neighborhood with community parks and proximity to the college as well as shopping, restaurants, and bus line. Don't hesitate or it will be gone!

This perfect home away from home is waiting for you! Enjoy the peaceful lake located in the foothills of the North Cascade Mountains with a serene view of Mount Baker. This community offers a plethora of fun, including 2 heated swimming pools, 2 hot tubs, a large clubhouse with games & entertainment provided, covered grills, picnic benches, beach volleyball, boat launch, kayak storage, multiple playgrounds, 18 hole mini golf, disk golf, tennis court, horseshoe pits, dog runs & more! This place really has it all whether you are looking to go fishing, paddle boarding, kayaking, swimming or just sit by a fire and enjoy the great outdoors. This lot offers an adorable trailer with 296 sq ft room addition plus a shed & comfort station close by!

VIEW VIEW VIEW Bask in the morning sun as you enjoy the sunrises over the Shelter Bay Marina w/views of the Cascade Mountains. The sunny exposure home features something for everyone w/an open floor plan; main level living; vaulted ceilings; spacious kitchen; gas fireplaces on main & lower level; large living room; 2-decks; oversized garage w/separate work shop; great room guest suite on the lower level w/bath & bedroom; lots of windows allowing the sun rays to penetrate the home w/an abundance of natural light for an experience only to be eclipsed by the fantastic sunrises and changes in the sky color as the sun sets in the evening. Amenities: swimming pools; tennis; clubhouse; golf course; 2 private beaches; marina; and boat ramp.

Welcome to Alpine Fairway Villa! Charming one level Condo in Eaglemont offering open floor plan, living room & open vaulted ceiling, large dining room w/ slider to patio to truly enjoy manicured yard w/ privacy and nature. Large kitchen w/ like new stainless-steel appliances & quartz counters and open to cozy family room w/ fireplace. Spacious owner suite w/walk-in shower, jetted tub, separate dressing area with plenty of closets. Laundry room leads to garage with shelving & workshop area. Newer furnace & Air conditioner. Sq.footage per Assessor, builder said 1500 + sq.ft Buyer to verify!! HOA dues include building insurance, landscape maintenance & exterior painting & roof.

Welcome to this beautifully updated home nestled in a serene country setting, just minutes away from downtown Mount Vernon. Open floor plan with large windows to allow a lot of natural light. Newly renovated kitchen, modern cabinets and brand new stainless steel appliances with detached coffee bar. This single-level home with a basement has 3 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms and office space offers plenty versatile living and storage space, office could be used as another bedroom! Updates galore! New roof in 2023, fresh exterior paint, new flooring, and a fresh coat of interior paint. Partially fenced, with a cozy fire pit, perfect for gatherings with friends. Lots of gardening space as well! This home is truly a must-see.

Absolutely gorgeous Conway farmhouse with 1800/sf shop on private .91acre. Tucked behind a tall hedge & iron gate for privacy, this 2360/sf 4 bed, 2.5 bath home exudes charm at every turn...from the claw foot tubs to the covered front porch; from the double-sided fireplace to the ceiling-height cabinetry, you'll appreciate every detail of this exceptionally well done home. Wide-plank LVP flooring, all new laundry, kitchen, & baths. Kitchen features quartz counters, stainless appliances. Huge living rm w/two seating areas. Primary suite w/tons of storage & gorgeous private bath. 3 guest beds (2 share a Jack & Jill half-bath). Unfinished basement provides storage & craft space galore. 30x60 shop w/220 power, air compressor, RV parking/power.

Fantastic Opportunity! Excellent 4 plex zoned Commercial Business District in the heart of Anacortes. The building is situated in the middle of a large 10, 492 SF lot with ample onsite parking, street parking, and alley. Just one block off Commercial Ave affords a nice walk to numerous restaurants, shopping, waterfront, and many other amenities that the very desirable Anacortes community is so sought after for. The building while in its original condition is in good shape given the caring long term tenants. Two 2beds 1bath and, two 1bed 1 bath. All feature nice kitchens w/dishwashers, dining, ample living rooms, and individual laundry. New roof installed. Please do not disturb the tenants.
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Beautiful 1.8 acre Fidalgo Island, Anacortes property with spectacular water and mountain views. Just one hour and fifteen minutes from Seattle, this rare gem resides on a private, dead-end street in the Estates at Summit Park and one of the few pieces of undeveloped property in an established community. The property has been cleared and prepped for your building project including water and power to the property and a completed perc test for septic. Enjoy peaceful nature walks on miles of maintained private trails, Kayaking in the bay or a picnic on the private expansive beach with views of Similk Bay. An incredible opportunity to build your dream home is awaiting you!
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Nestled on 9.83 acres of rare flat farm land, this Cape Cod style home with picturesque landscape exudes the charm of the 1940s era while offering modern comforts. Upon stepping inside you'll find hardwood floors & exposed beams that add character to the interior, while large windows flood the space with natural light, creating an inviting and airy feel. The remodeled kitchen has newer appliances nestled amidst plenty of cabinetry for storage offering both functionality and appeal. The living areas are cozy yet spacious, perfect for hosting gatherings or unwinding by the wood fireplace. Whether you're savoring a meal on the porch or simply taking in the sights and sounds this of rural life, this home offers a timeless retreat

Nice rambler style Duplex in Burlington! Each unit boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 3/4 bath, 1080 sq ft of living space, kitchen with all appliances including stack washer and dryer, covered front patio, fenced backyard and a one car garage. Located on a dead end street, close to shopping, restaurants, I5 and more!

Youll want to live in this stunning 3262sqft home on a beautifully treed, shy 5 acres. The main house boasts a spacious primary suite, opulent walk-in closet & lux 5pc en-suite. Theres so much room in the living room & dont miss the work space w/ 220v-is it a commercial kitchen, gym space or craft/studio you decide! Remodeled 2124sqft ADU: 3 bds, 2 ba, bonus storage theater? Wine cellar? Ideal set up for guests. So many outdoor amenities: 220v, chicken coop, playsets, dog kennel, multiple spigots, a stunning iron gazebo & water fountain ready for you to transform it into the perfect oasis or event venue. The possibilities are endless with this one of a kind gem!

Welcome home to this beautifully remodeled craftsman home. Enjoy simple living on an easy to maintain lot and home. Walking distance to many downtown amenities. This home has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home and wall to wall carpet in the upstairs bedrooms. Stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops. High efficient heat pump and AC perfect for the cold winters and hot summers. Backyard has two sheds and room for entertaining. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity.

Awesome property on shy 2 acres! You'll love the privacy this home provides. 2 bed/1.75 bath in home with an amazing Detached (42'x48' SF) Shop with Kitchenette and 3/4 bath. Office in home could be used as a 3rd Bedroom (non conforming). Great Room concept with Kitchen open to Living space and vaulted gives you spaciousness for entertaining and relaxing. Lots of windows bringing the outdoors inside. New deck surrounds 2 sides. Metal Roof on both buildings. Attached 2 car garage + shop/garage parking gives you up to 6 car parking on site! Never worry about power here with a 24kW generator on site. You'll love living on this peaceful property! Welcome Home!
